    "_postman_id": "studypro-api-collection",
    "name": "StudyPro API Collection",
    "description": "Complete API collection for StudyPro (Flash Site Cursos) e-learning platform.\n\nThis collection includes all endpoints for:\n- Authentication (Login, Register, Token Verification)\n- User Management\n- Course Management\n- Course Modules\n- Lessons\n- System Status\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT authentication. After login, the token is automatically saved in the collection variables.\n\n## Environment Variables\n- `base_url`: The API base URL (default: http://localhost:8180)\n- `auth_token`: JWT token (automatically set after login)\n- `admin_email`: Default admin email\n- `admin_password`: Default admin password",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
