              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify"]
            },
            "description": "Verify if the current JWT token is valid and get user information.\n\n**Headers Required:**\n- Authorization: Bearer {token}\n\n**Success Response:**\n```json\n{\n    \"success\": true,\n    \"user\": {\n        \"id\": \"123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000\",\n        \"name\": \"Administrador\",\n        \"email\": \"admin@estudos.com\",\n        \"role\": \"admin\",\n        \"avatar\": null\n    }\n}\n```"
